column2: Rule 1: {fullname words <= 5, description length is To much} -> {fullname words <= 3}

Rule 2: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much, #followers is A
  bit} -> {fullname words <= 2, #posts is One or less, #follows is A bit}

Rule 3: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much, #follows is To
  much} -> {#posts is Medium, #followers is To much}

Rule 4: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much, #follows is A bit}
  -> {fullname words <= 2, #posts is One or less, #followers is A bit}

Rule 5: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much, #posts is Medium}
  -> {#follows is To much, #followers is To much}

Rule 6: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much, #posts is One or
  less} -> {fullname words <= 2, #follows is A bit, #followers is A bit}

Rule 7: {fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is Any, description length
  is To much} -> {profile pic, fullname words <= 0, fullname words <= 1, fullname words <= 2,
  name==username, description length is Medium, external URL, #posts is One or less, #posts is
  Medium, #posts is To much, private, #follows is A bit, #follows is Medium, #follows is To much,
  #followers is A bit, #followers is Medium, #followers is To much}

Rule 8: {fullname words <= 2, fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To
  much, #followers is To much} -> {fullname words <= 1, name==username}

Rule 9: {fullname words <= 1, fullname words <= 2, fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5,
  description length is To much} -> {name==username, #followers is To much}

Rule 11: {profile pic, fullname words <= 3, fullname words <= 5, description length is To much} ->
  {#followers is To much}
